Two cocktail destinations, one Indian spirited gin.

We're thrilled our cross-continental collaboration is being loved world over— and our sights are set on the horizon for more exciting things to come. Cheers!

You hear it before you feel it—the fizz, the pour, the pause between moments. It’s not just a drink but a sound that says: the weekend has arrived. 

Sparkling wine meets Perry Road Peru in a glass that hums with promise.

#StrangerAndSons #PerryRoadPeru #IndianGin

A pour that catches the light just right. Pink, chilled, and impossible to ignore.

Perry Road Peru—your season’s most refreshing sip.

#StrangerAndSons #PerryRoadPeru
latestPosts.alt: Photo by Stranger & Sons on June 18, 2025. May be an image of cocktail, grapefruit and text.

latestPosts.caption:
The season’s allure? A chilled glass of Perry Road Peru, topped with soda water or a splash of sparkling wine.

It’s more than a drink—it’s your summer ritual in the making.

#StrangerAndSons #PerryRoadPeru #SummerOnIce

Freshness you can see—before the first sip. Infused with luscious guavas, Perry Road Peru is ease, bottled and ready to serve. Just pour over ice and you’re there!

#StrangerAndSons #PerryRoadPeru #SummerOnIce

One spirit. Four serves.

Serve it over ice, with a splash of tonic, a pour of sparkling wine, or a slow stir of sweet vermouth. And always, our signature salt-sugar-spice rim to seal the moment.

#StrangerAndSons #PerryRoadPeru #IndianGin

The ice settles. The bubbles rise. Before you know it, it’s gone again. 

Effortlessly fresh, impossible to put down. 

#StrangerAndSons #PerryRoadPeru #SummerOnIce

A hand outstretched, a moment suspended. The kind of pour that draws you in—before the ice even thinks of melting. 

Your glass is waiting. Have you picked up your bottle yet? 

#StrangerAndSons #PerryRoadPeru #SummerOnIce

One clink, and just like that—summer’s in session.

Find your bottle of Perry Road Peru at the store closest to you and don’t forget to pair it with our signature salt-sugar-spice mix for a finish that lingers.

#StrangerAndSons #PerryRoadPeru #SummerOnIce

Golden hours, and glasses that never empty.

Perry Road Peru is here to turn your summer into something worth savouring. Refreshing, pink, and made for the kind of summer you hope never ends. 

#StrangerAndSons #PerryRoadPeru #SummerOnIce

Peru, spice, and plenty of ice! Sip into the summer and savour the most refreshing pour. Don’t forget that final flourish—our signature salt-sugar-chilli mix.

Grab your bottles now in Mumbai, Pune, Goa, and Gurugram.
